data.description: This is an estate sale. This home is a fixer-upper but has so much potential to be the home you are looking for. The home is handicap assessable. Huge rooms, hallway, doorways, and bathrooms. It has a jack-and-jill bath between 2 large bedrooms a huge bonus room, unfinished partial basement. The house sits on 3.4 acres plus or minus. A circular driveway that comes in handy for large party parking. Items in pictures are from the Estate sale and will be removed.
